OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear spells
OL,6,Fand variable cloud in the evening with
OL,7,Fa few showers in places. Largely dry
OL,8,Fbut cloudy overnight with a few
OL,9,Fshowers again towards morning. Patchy
OL,10,Ffrost in places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FIt will be quite cool with
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells and scattered
OL,14,Fheavy showers. Chance of overnight
OL,15,Ffrost in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
